        <p style="margin-top: 24px;">See also: <a href="/alternatives/majestic/" class="accent">Majestic alternatives</a>, <a href="/modules/content-seo/" class="accent">Content SEO module</a>, or <a href="/pricing/" class="accent">theStacc pricing</a>.</p>
